      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garaged, kept spotless, and treated with total love. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feel to it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
