    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a definitive example of JDM engineering, preserved in showroom condition. Under the hood lies the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six, featuring an overbuilt iron block and sequential forced induction for seamless power delivery. Mated to the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains unmodified and mechanically flawless. The chassis retains its original double-wishbone suspension geometry, providing the precise, analog feedback expected of an A80-generation flagship. This is a numbers-matching, investment-grade vehicle with optimal compression and zero structural oxidation.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
