    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a factory-fresh luster that must be seen to be believed. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, free of any stone chips, scratches, or swirls, and has been recently treated with a professional multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero signs of wear, the carpets are pristine, and the original scent remains. Every electronic feature and luxury amenity functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by the dealership, ensuring a drive that is as tight and responsive as the day it was first delivered. This vehicle comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a detailed folder of every maintenance receipt. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade investment that has been pampered from day one.",
      "price": 48900.0,
