    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS to deliver a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by a factory variable M differential lock. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension geometry remains true with OE-spec bushings, preserving the communicative steering rack and 50/50 weight distribution. Finished with flawless paint depth and a pristine interior, this example exhibits zero mechanical lash and represents the pinnacle of the analog driving era.",
